        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for a contribution ["On the so-called ""auditory-sac"" of cirripedes", <hi rend="italic">Nat. Hist. Rev.</hi> (1863): 115–16; <hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 2: 85–7]. Is sending a proof.</p> 
            <p>This year’s lecture to working men to be devoted to CD’s book.</p>
        </abstract>
